{"tid":1032996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子赴台港感染公廁的洗手機及洗手液食肉菌變爛臉","createTime":"2019-02-22T19:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T23:15:56.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c130f15fc7b77c60ca21c47247ae707cab63afd","tid":1032996,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190222/640_3c0d0c85143eed52fbe69f750b757195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190222%2F640_3c0d0c85143eed52fbe69f750b757195.jpg&h=215f7d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威瑟斯赴台港工作後返國開始出現紅疹，醫師證實她感染食肉菌。《IG》<br />\n<br />\n公共廁所的洗手液是殺菌還是細菌的溫床？美國一名女子赴台灣及香港做媒體巡迴，返國後身上開始出現紅疹，臉上更出現血瘡，半張臉被細菌啃食變得坑坑疤疤，最後證實是因為「食肉菌」作怪，而醫師證實她的確是位工作巡迴時感染。有專家指出，這種細菌來自公共廁所的洗手機及洗手液。<br />\n<br />\n《People》、《觀察家報》、《The State》綜合報導，美國南卡羅萊納（The South Carolinian）33歲好萊塢特技女演員威瑟斯（Rachel Star Withers）一月份為了工作赴台灣及香港做媒體巡迴，返國後身體開始出現紅色腫塊，起初臉上只是出現了一塊塊的紅腫，但沒想到之後狀況越來越嚴重，紅腫的地方逐漸腐爛成坑洞，範圍也擴大至半張臉，並且不斷感到噁心而食不下嚥。<br />\n<br />\n威瑟斯開始求診尋找原因，在看過多位醫師之後都診斷她是嚴重痤瘡，內服外用的藥都試過卻無改善，最後有一名醫師確診她感染大量克雷伯氏菌（Klebsiella Oxytoca），並指出該病菌離開腸道就會攻擊人類的肺部導致腹痛，並導致肺炎或尿道感染，對免疫系統較弱的人來說，甚至有可能致命，醫師也證實她的確是在亞洲巡迴工作時感染克雷伯氏菌。<br />\n<br />\n對此，美國清潔專家普羅達諾瓦（Ralitsa Prodanova）指出，克雷伯氏菌有機會是來自餐廳、公共廁所等開放空間所提供的洗手液，她表示壁掛式的給皂機若沒有經仔細清洗，就有可能成為細菌的溫床，她建議大家應攜帶慣用的抗菌洗手液，避免受到細菌感染。<br />\n<br />\n此外，亞利桑那大學微生物博士杰巴（Charles Gerba）進行的研究也指出，隨機檢驗296間餐廳的給皂機中，顯示有15%染出有害細菌，包括耐抗生素的大腸桿菌，沙門氏菌和威瑟斯所感染的克雷伯氏菌。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190222/1522046/?fbclid=IwAR19ObhvoNhBwweuO5WnzVmh6SeLQgblw96PzjbSEWWkkdLB_ilhiFy1yt8&amp;utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1522046%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR19ObhvoNhBwweuO5WnzVmh6SeLQgblw96PzjbSEWWkkdLB_ilhiFy1yt8%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=8ed841a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1522046%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR19ObhvoNhBwweuO5WnzVmh6SeLQgblw96PzjbSEWWkkdLB_ilhiFy1yt8%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&h=4fb2faeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190222/1522046/?fbclid=IwAR19ObhvoNhBwweuO5WnzVmh6SeLQgblw96PzjbSEWWkkdLB_ilhiFy1yt8&amp;utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook</a>"},{"pid":"9c149c8f33fd6af74fb37904c5c5bd13bb378234","tid":1032996,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:32:06.000Z","msg":"公廁咁臭都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲垃圾咁大個人都會痾到成地尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4d913b12202b3baaf6bb992567193a6ba6bfd2","tid":1032996,"uid":51411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:42:43.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 以後唔用出面廁所洗手液<br />\n仲污漕過唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83510acb2273418ab4d4d3dfa0cb5eff35bb1eb0","tid":1032996,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f4d913b12202b3baaf6bb992567193a6ba6bfd2","tid":1032996,"uid":51411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:42:43.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 以後唔用出面廁所洗手液<br />\n仲污漕過唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T22:15:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗手好過洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54badec9963638ca50f72f6ada7551ee1f2df25d","tid":1032996,"uid":33825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T22:25: